nce Suite</a></i> (1989)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #EEEEEE;\">Choral</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Hashkiveinu_(Bernstein)\" title=\"Hashkiveinu (Bernstein)\">Hashkiveinu</a></i> (1945)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Chichester_Psalms\" title=\"Chichester Psalms\">Chichester Psalms</a></i> (1965)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Missa_Brevis_(Bernstein)\" title=\"Missa Brevis (Bernstein)\">Missa Brevis</a> (1988)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #EEEEEE;\">Vocal</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>\"<a href=\"/wiki/So_Pretty_(Leonard_Bernstein_song)\" title=\"So Pretty (Leonard Bernstein song)\">So pretty</a>\"</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Songfest:_A_Cycle_of_American_Poems_for_Six_Singers_and_Orchestra\" title=\"Songfest: A Cycle of American Poems for Six Singers and Orchestra\">Songfest: A Cycle of American Poems for Six Singers and Orchestra</a></i> (1977)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #EEEEEE;\">Piano</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Four_Anniversaries\" title=\"Four Anniversaries\">Four Anniversaries</a></i> (1948)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/13_Anniversaries\" title=\"13 Anniversaries\">13 Anniversaries</a></i> (1988)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%;background: #EEEEEE;\">Other compositions</th><td class=\"navbox